Class SortAndSearch.BinaryTree<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • severinnitsche.com.github.SortAndSearch.BinaryTree<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Enclosing class:
    SortAndSearch

    public static class SortAndSearch.BinaryTree<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>
    The Binary Tree class provides methods to populate a Binary Tree, get the root value and both sub-trees

    The use of a enhanced for loop returns the items in ascending order but is to use with care since it destroyes the tree structure
